<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 09:12:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>交通银行一季度利润增长1.44%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-bank-communications-q1-profit-rises-144-2024-04-26/</link><description>中国交通银行股份有限公司 (BoCom) 公布，在经济放缓的情况下，第一季度净利润增长 1.44%。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 09:10:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-bank-communications-q1-profit-rises-144-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>中信证券一季度利润下降8.5%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-citic-securities-posts-85-fall-first-quarter-profit-2024-04-26/</link><description>中国最大的券商中信证券周五公布第一季度净利润下降8.5%。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 08:57:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-citic-securities-posts-85-fall-first-quarter-profit-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>斯里兰卡将把中国建设的机场管理权交给印度和俄罗斯公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/sri-lanka-hand-management-china-built-airport-india-russia-companies-2024-04-26/</link><description>周五内阁声明称，斯里兰卡将把中国耗资 2.09 亿美元建造的机场的管理权移交给两家印度和俄罗斯公司，该岛国试图减少国有企业的损失。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 08:36:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/sri-lanka-hand-management-china-built-airport-india-russia-companies-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>华为的智能汽车技术为汽车制造商提供了在中国销售的途径</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/huaweis-smart-car-tech-offers-automakers-route-china-sales-2024-04-26/</link><description>华为只用了四年时间就成为智能汽车技术领域的一股力量，在应对贸易制裁对其智能手机业务造成的破坏的同时，还开发了北京车展宠儿的驾驶辅助系统。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 08:04:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/huaweis-smart-car-tech-offers-automakers-route-china-sales-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>独家：碧桂园计划下半年提出债务重组计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-plans-present-debt-revamp-plan-second-half-sources-say-2024-04-26/</link><description>两名消息人士称，碧桂园已告知其一些海外债权人，计划在今年下半年提出债务重组提案，因为这家陷入困境的开发商正在努力避免清算申请。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 07:05:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-plans-present-debt-revamp-plan-second-half-sources-say-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国干邑白兰地销量推动人头马君度第四季度销量创佳绩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/remy-cointreau-reports-better-than-expected-q4-sales-2024-04-26/</link><description>周五，人头马君度股价上涨 6.8%，此前该公司公布第四季度销售额降幅远小于预期，并称中国的“显着增长”帮助其干邑部门意外增长。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 05:33:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/remy-cointreau-reports-better-than-expected-q4-sales-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>北京车展：主题与亮点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/beijing-auto-show-themes-highlights-2024-04-26/</link><description>中国最大的车展在北京开幕，各大品牌展示了他们最新的电动汽车（EV），突显出全球最大的汽车市场已经处于全电动状态，并且不会回头。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 05:07:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/beijing-auto-show-themes-highlights-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>香港3月房价上涨1.1% 近一年来首次上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-march-home-prices-up-11-first-rise-nearly-year-2024-04-26/</link><description>在金融城市取消限制以提振疲弱的房地产市场后，香港私人住宅价格在3月份扭转了连续10个月的下跌趋势，较2月份上涨1.1%。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 03:51:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kong-march-home-prices-up-11-first-rise-nearly-year-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>博世将在中国城市推出城市自动驾驶导航功能</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bosch-launch-urban-navigate-on-autopilot-functions-chinese-cities-2024-04-26/</link><description>博世移动部门董事长马库斯·海恩 (Markus Heyn) 周五表示，博世 (ROBSCJ.UL) 将于 5 月份通过其先进的驾驶辅助系统推出城市自动驾驶导航 (NOA) 功能。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 03:18:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bosch-launch-urban-navigate-on-autopilot-functions-chinese-cities-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>随着与贸易伙伴的紧张局势加剧，中国通过关税法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-passes-tariff-law-tensions-with-trading-partners-simmer-2024-04-26/</link><description>中国周五通过了一项法律，这使得其最大的贸易伙伴毫无疑问可以反击，如果他们对世界第二大经济体的出口征收关税，华盛顿和布鲁塞尔就工业产能过剩问题将矛头指向北京。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 02:14:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-passes-tariff-law-tensions-with-trading-partners-simmer-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>北京市将补贴国产人工智能芯片 目标到2027年实现自力更生</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/beijing-city-subsidise-domestic-ai-chips-targets-self-reliance-by-2027-2024-04-26/</link><description>随着中国寻求发展半导体产业并减少对外国技术的依赖，北京市当局宣布对购买国产人工智能（AI）芯片的企业提供补贴。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 01:58:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/beijing-city-subsidise-domestic-ai-chips-targets-self-reliance-by-2027-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>股市面临9月份以来最糟糕的一个月，日元跟随日本央行波动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-26/</link><description>周五，全球股市摇摇欲坠，正面临自 9 月份以来最糟糕的一个月，尽管期货市场预测强劲的科技股盈利将在当天晚些时候引发华尔街的缓解性反弹，从而帮助交易员挽回部分损失。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 01:49:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯在北京提出美国对中国支持俄罗斯的担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-meet-chinese-counterpart-wang-yi-beijing-2024-04-26/</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周五对中国对俄罗斯军事的支持表示担忧，这是威胁全球最大经济体之间近期改善关系的众多问题之一。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 00:39:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-meet-chinese-counterpart-wang-yi-beijing-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>日元突然飙升后回落</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-its-weakest-decades-boj-meets-2024-04-26/</link><description>日元兑美元和其他货币短暂上涨后，周五下跌，令交易员高度警惕日本央行在最新会议上维持利率不变后日本货币当局买入的迹象。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 00:23:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-its-weakest-decades-boj-meets-2024-04-26/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示全球经济今年剩余时间将保持增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/global-economy-set-stay-roll-rest-year-2024-04-26/</link><description>路透社对经济学家的一项调查显示，全球经济可能会在今年剩余时间乃至 2025 年保持强劲势头，打破此前对经济放缓的预期。经济学家表示，增长强于预期的可能性大于疲软。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 00:22:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/global-economy-set-stay-roll-rest-year-2024-04-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>